{"tid":244592,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友好撚固執 可以點？","createTime":"2017-05-15T14:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T00:35:26.000Z","uid":82363,"like":1,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"230ed664b55f501a1de3f2c5d198d651f4443393","tid":244592,"uid":82363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:14:53.000Z","msg":"黎緊暑期我會同屋企人去一星期旅行，同男朋友講咗之後佢發哂癲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事關同男朋友係成日見，大家都係好痴身，但我都係同屋企人去下旅行啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我話除咗嗰一個星期唔係香港，其餘時間都可以見佢陪佢。就算去咗旅行，每日都會whatsapp同facetime，但佢都發哂脾氣話唔想我去旅行<br />\n我話只係想同屋企人去下旅行 周圍玩下 點解唔得 有咩問題，佢答我關佢撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 總之就係唔想我去<br />\n我完全唔知點同佢講落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de7877954ec57241bf89ac6eb74d209943cff49","tid":244592,"uid":4210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"8f5b577607b44d0597695aacac766c27b21dcaa8","tid":244592,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:19:08.000Z","msg":"你問下佢要唔要腸仔蛋"},{"pid":"986b11e60f9e5e7c5ed09911baf925516462f888","tid":244592,"uid":1042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"分手"},{"pid":"e90802fabea30e43d1dbd936f5cf6519bb35be1b","tid":244592,"uid":106597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:20:09.000Z","msg":"帶埋佢去"},{"pid":"c0aa406c1b40959cd44491b8d6ec02f5e1a26f18","tid":244592,"uid":45431,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:20:26.000Z","msg":"同佢講有種就跟埋去，無就收嗲"},{"pid":"b938e5f5faf34967a7aeaa7518c8071b348d68f5","tid":244592,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:20:39.000Z","msg":"同屋企人去已經咁<br />\n同朋友去會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa057873e7b7926e6c166d00b521403fe1a