到明係控制狂<br />\n你講咩佢都唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知佢可能係太愛我 太緊張我 <br />\n想我成日見佢陪佢 可以多啲相處時間<br />\n但我都只係同屋企人去一個星期旅行啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過如果佢都係咁固執咁點算？"},{"pid":"9bc7ef9b601a3d68b4c142bbe7c626ea733cedd5","tid":244592,"uid":43641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"咁唔係固執 係on9"},{"pid":"c39da61105a6cf8ea23b99e86b23a9cd80a32935","tid":244592,"uid":82363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:56:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推到樓主男朋友睇到個post然後反省下<br />\n利申依加女朋友去咗美國一個月後返 我應該要跳樓？<br />\n凡事唔好迫太緊會有反效果</blockquote><br />\n我真係好希望佢明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb041c2e61cc1e1181f2cd2834e4c8b22da98d0b","tid":244592,"uid":71209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:57:05.000Z","msg":"22歲都咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9be02c67714042de807d6da96371f233de6ada2","tid":244592,"uid":82363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男朋友未去過旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢去咗幾次台灣<br />\n但黎緊6月我同佢去日本旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf485c7d5d749bf0b6081bdc4b07635ce3137e1","tid":244592,"uid":70098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你男朋友有冇錢靚唔靚仔先？</blockquote><br />\n無錢 <br />\n係我眼中 佢係最靚仔<br />\n我好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我估你同男仔單獨出街<br />\n佢斬你全家都似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d2d3c034e53307dcfe302e2af5c960dc783788","tid":244592,"uid":60857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:58:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飛<br />\n傻鳩黎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係想分手呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你都唔撚明，而家就係叫你咪撚要依條仔呀！<br />\n痴身還痴身，佢而家係唔理你感受、自私又霸道！<br />\n佢有無諗過你同緊朋友/家人去玩，佢瘋狂打電話俾你，你同你身邊既人會有咩感受？<br />\n拍拖就代表你唔可以同其他人去玩？你又唔係去溝仔！而且佢憑咩唔俾你同屋企人去旅行？22歲唔係12歲wo，仲以為發下脾氣就咩都有？<br />\n俾著我係你就屌鳩佢然後唔柒理佢！<br />\n<br />\n利申：絲"},{"pid":"92cf28db47e5baa181c05f0e9db547b525636cdd","tid":244592,"uid":82363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要同你講關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你甘心成世都冇哂自由咩<br />\n同屋企人去都唔比，你男朋友世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快d叫佢黎睇呢個post</blockquote><br />\n佢有上連登，我好撚希望佢睇到呢個post之後會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺到明係控制狂<br />\n你講咩佢都唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知佢可能係太愛我 太緊張我 <br />\n想我成日見佢陪佢 可以多啲相處時間<br />\n但我都只係同屋企人去一個星期旅行啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過如果佢都係咁固執咁點算？</blockquote><br />\n唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人連機票都買埋，我又諗唔到有咩原因係我唔應該同屋企人去旅行"},{"pid":"b8de511fa16cf77ef74459fbffb169697f55cb6d","tid":244592,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男朋友未去過旅行？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢去咗幾次台灣<br />\n但黎緊6月我同佢去日本旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nbook左野未<br />\nbook左就諗定分左手比番幾多旅費啦"},{"pid":"be277501b9b48d680cd94a03bd286dc27cc71728","tid":244592,"uid":60857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要同你講關我撚事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔通你甘心成世都冇哂自由咩<br />\n同屋企人去都唔比，你男朋友世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n快d叫佢黎睇呢個post</blockquote><br />\n佢有上連登，我好撚希望佢睇到呢個post之後會明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n擺到明係控制狂<br />\n你講咩佢都唔會聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知佢可能係太愛我 太緊張我 <br />\n想我成日見佢陪佢 可以多啲相處時間<br />\n但我都只係同屋企人去一個星期旅行啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你有冇諗過如果佢都係咁固執咁點算？</blockquote><br />\n唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屋企人連機票都買埋，我又諗唔到有咩原因係我唔應該同屋企人去旅行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌因為你同屋企人去玩係好撚正常好合理既事，點會搵到理由唔去。<br />\n你話無假放個d就話"},{"pid":"1eb6e425d9d8287c3c0589342b24256675b467c8","tid":244592,"uid":93830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:04:50.000Z","msg":"On9配on9天生一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d9a48f11b7bc0eabdf02180cce2beaf119b2e2b","tid":244592,"uid":89843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"同我果個一模一樣<br />\n慢慢你就會無哂朋友<br />\n同屋企人遠離哂<br />\n生活好快就得返佢一個<br />\n想走又走吾到（因為走左就真係乜都無哂）<br />\n你接受到就得"},{"pid":"24ae537570bb35025b6d1295e28629d8ba54b587","tid":244592,"uid":89843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:06:30.000Z","msg":"唔"}